The paper deals with image and object classification datasets, which suggests that it belongs to the computer vision (cs.CV) sub-category. The use of statistical Extreme Value Theory (EVT) and hypothesis testing also suggests that it may belong to the machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI) sub-categories. The use of image datasets also suggests that it may belong to the multimedia (cs.MM) sub-category. Finally, the use of classification algorithms suggests that it may belong to the information retrieval (cs.IR) sub-category.
